keyFacts: The document is email correspondence regarding a subpoena to Lockheed Martin in the case United States v. Maxwell.
The emails discuss technical issues accessing a secure USAFx folder for sharing produced materials.
A Paralegal Specialist from the U.S. Attorney's Office, SDNY, was involved in setting up the folder access.
The files to be produced were outlined in attached correspondence and were to be Bates labeled.
